        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR2e0001-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T17:55:45.64+09:00">季康子决心按庶民私田的地亩征取地税和兵役、摇役，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T17:56:44.34+09:00">再次进行变革。事前派遣冉有征询老师仲尼的意见，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T17:56:55.511+09:00">仲尼不答。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T17:57:03.546+09:00">私下仲尼对冉有说道：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T17:57:11.432+09:00">＂冉求，你过来！</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T17:57:18.736+09:00">你没有听说过吗？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T17:57:26.069+09:00">先代圣王分配土地，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T17:57:42.255+09:00">按地质肥瘦优劣定出授田的数批等差，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T17:57:55.577+09:00">根据庶民的年龄体力定期授予土地．，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T17:58:06.44+09:00">征取不同差额的地税，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:03:39.267+09:00">用以均平近郊、远郊以及甸、稍、县等不同地带民役征用的差拭；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:03:39.286+09:00">这祥，丧偶男女、孤儿、残疾者，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:03:39.29+09:00">国家向庶民征收宅土税，以每个民户的实际收入为基础，并审最宅旁有元按规定要求种有桑麻；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:03:39.304+09:00">民役征用民户男丁，审查他叶是否属千不役年龄的老幼。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:08:10.827+09:00">只有在发生战争、出</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:04:52.929+09:00">否则不征。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:05:25.463+09:00">战时，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:06:27.654+09:00">田一井征收</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:06:39.44+09:00">干柴一铅，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:06:47.408+09:00">饲草一秉，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:06:53.027+09:00">小米一伈，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:06:59.763+09:00">不能超出此数。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:07:10.723+09:00">先代圣王认为这巳满足需要，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:07:20+09:00">如季孙子需要税田之法，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:07:26.977+09:00">则有周公姐旦制定的上述籍田之制；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:07:32.032+09:00">如试图违反旧法，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:07:38.953+09:00">则可随心所欲地向庶民征收赋役，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:07:41.43+09:00">那又何必征淘我的意见呢？”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2e0001_tls_002-93a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-30T18:08:27.838+09:00">现军队调发时才征服力役，</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
